---
title: Thai Massaman Rice with Roasted Eggplant, Mushrooms and Bamboo Shoots
description: For this Thai Massaman rice, we combined the creaminess of peanut butter (our secret ingredient!) and coconut milk against the fresh tanginess of cilantro and lime. Roasting the eggplant makes this dish extra special!
